hed manhunt for suspected kidnappers of a Chinese expatriate in the state. May 31, 2016 In "News" The Ebonyi Police Command has rescued the two kidnapped Chinese nationals who were abducted by unknown gunmen at a road construction site in Ohaozara Local Government Area of the state on Wednesday. April 28, 2019 In "News" By Simon Ebegbulem BENIN—A Chinese expatriate attached to the BUA Cement Company in Okpella, Etsako East Local Government Area of Edo State, was abducted on Monday, while an officer of the Nigeria Security and Civil Defence Corps, NSCDC, attached to him was killed by the suspected kidnappers. It was gathered… June 7, 2017 In "Business"